episodes.title: KQED's A Closer Look: People's Temple, November 20, 1978
episodes.description: A look at the People's Temple tragedy in Guyana, featuring Belva Davis, Dr. Carleton Goodlett, Pamela Youn, Phil Bronstein, Clem Deamicis, Nancy Steidtmann, Al Mills, Rollin Post, George Moscone, Willie Brown, Phil Tracy, Al Mills and Bob Graham.
